race.comment: MADE YOU LOOK (3) is long overdue for a win, finishing in the minors at her last three starts, the latest jumping from this same box when second in a Grade 6 at this track (19.45). Rates a top chance. HARDLY EASY (8) has hit the frame here at the last two runs, most recently finishing third beaten 6 lengths (16.97). Expected to feature. FARMOR DEFIANT (2) turned in a moderate effort last time when eighth at Q Lakeside over 352m behind Alpha One (20.63) in a Grade 6. Leading chance. REVA TWIST (4) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.
